## Core image types, i.e. types the core can create ...

foreach {n cando itype channels} {
    0 {}     grey8     {luma}
    1   NYI  grey16    {luma}
    2   NYI  grey32    {luma}
    3 {}     float     {value}
    4   NYI  fpcomplex {real imaginary}
    5   NYI  rgb       {red green blue}
    6   NYI  rgba      {red green blue alpha}
